Ngigaayung ngarrubagi-yung Herodias anubani-yung ngu-magaa ngiga ngarra-ngarrimarayung. Nguynju yadhu ngigaayung ngarra-ngaḻaynjinyung ngi-yamaa nubagi-wuy na-Herod-guy, “Nimbiiyn anubani-yung ngayawi-wuy ana-yinag na-John, yaani-wuy arrwar ama-plate-duj,” ngi-yamayn.
