Anubanila-wala niga na-Jesus ni-yanggi, anubani-yung ni-yanggi bagala-yung ama-madhaḻag-baj ana-wurugu-waj ana-Galilee-waj. Anubani-yung ni-yanggi arrwar ama-magabang-guy marri niindhadhi bagu.
